Boxercise, or sometimes referred to as Boxercise workout, is a high-intensity aerobic exercise. Caloric expenditure varies among individuals based on factors such as personal differences, exercise intensity, and duration. Generally, boxercise training is a full-body workout that provides high cardiovascular exercise and muscle endurance training.
